1. Ja razum*em šta mi govoriš. (I understand what you're telling me.)
2. *Razum*e se da ćeš biti tamo na vreme. (It goes without saying that you'll be there on time.)
3. Molim te, *razum*i moju situaciju. (Please, understand my situation.)
4. On ima *razum*evanja za tu decu. (He has sympathy for those children.)
5. Njegovo ponašanje nije bilo *razum*no. (His behavior wasn't reasonable.)
6. Nauči da koristiš *razum* i ne donosi ishitrene odluke. (Learn to use your brain and don't make rash decisions.)
7. *Razum*eli smo se bez reči. (We understood each other without words.)
8. Da li si *razum*eo šta je rekao? (Did you understand what he said?)
9. Potrebno je imati *razum*evanja za druge ljude. (It's necessary to have understanding for other people.)
10. Ponekad je teško *razum*eti šta drugi ljudi misle. (Sometimes it's hard to understand what other people are thinking.)